Geo-Coder-Bing
==============

This module provides an interface to the Bing Maps Geocoding API

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Encode
    JSON
    LWP::UserAgent
    Test::More
    URI

